        </item>
        <item>
            <title>iPhone 16 爆假機事件，先達回收商蝕 3 萬指生意難捱</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/22/iphone-16-4/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-16-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/22/iphone-16-4/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 05:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1264676</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>iPhone 16 系列日前正式開賣，先達廣場內發生回收商收到假機的騙案，令其中一家店損失了高達 3 萬元。涉事店家指出，這是開賣首日便發生的事件，回收的兩部 iPhone 16 Pro Max 外觀與真機極為相似，連盒內配件都非常完整，令店主慨嘆「生意難做」。</p><p>一名店主在 Facebook 上分享了這宗騙案的詳情，並附上假機的照片，兩部手機的包裝盒、配件及手機的外觀都與真機幾乎無異，難以分辨。這次事件令得主感到無奈，並表示手機市場的詐騙手法日益高明，回收商需更加謹慎。</p><p>據瞭解，該事件發生於旺角先達廣場一間回收商店內。該店主表示，事發時因店舖人多擁擠，工作繁忙，未能即時仔細檢查，導致收到兩部假機，隨後發現損失高達 3 萬元。涉事店鋪已立即報警處理。</p><p>警方接獲報案後，根據初步調查結果，將案件列為「以欺騙手段取得財產」，並交由旺角刑事調查隊第二隊跟進調查。據悉，報案人稱早前在西洋菜南街的另一商場內，以 24,000 元購入兩部手機，並在亞皆老街另一商場打算轉售時發現它們是樣辦機。至今警方尚未拘捕涉案人士，案件仍在調查中。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264677" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240922115649-641x580.jpg" alt="" width="641" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240922115649-641x580.jpg 641w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240922115649.jpg 994w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 641px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264678" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460521946_9202849301-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460521946_9202849301-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460521946_9202849301.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460630596_9202849667-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460630596_9202849667-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460630596_9202849667.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264680" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460722730_9202849267-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460722730_9202849267-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460722730_9202849267.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264681" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460455930_9202850001-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460455930_9202850001-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460455930_9202850001.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460541724_9202849634-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460541724_9202849634-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460541724_9202849634.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264683" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460456818_9202849401-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460456818_9202849401-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460456818_9202849401.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264684" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460488846_9202849367-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460488846_9202849367-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/460488846_9202849367.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=920285066783752&amp;id=100064068004143">Facebook</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/20/iphone-16-pro-iphone-16/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】iPhone 16 / 16 Pro   新實體影相按鈕 + 大量新相機鏡頭試相 + 無線充電實試</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/18/iphone16proreview/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 Pro Max 詳細開箱影片，並非只「多了顆掣」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/iphone-16-%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97-pro-max-%e5%a4%96%e5%aa%92%e4%b8%8a%e6%89%8b%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac-%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b-18-%e5%80%8b%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd-apple-watch-s10-%e5%8f%8a-airpods-4/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 系列 Pro Max 外媒上手評測，港人最愛 18 個功能</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/22/iphone-16-4/mobile-phone/">iPhone 16 爆假機事件，先達回收商蝕 3 萬指生意難捱</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
